review_blob: Sweet for a stout but by no means a sweet beer. Very Strong notes of peanut butter in the aroma but the peanut is more subtle in taste
beer_name: Belching Beaver Peanut Butter Milk Stout

review_blob: The aroma has strong notes of vanilla that make it smell just like Cream Soda! since its a light body beer its the vanilla is the main flavor which will not make this beer everyones favorite but it is definitely one of mine
Crisp light flavor accented with a tart strawberry flavor. Aroma is a bit odd but still an incredible beer!!
